 index.html | 6 +++---
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/index.html b/index.html
index 4b139b0..8f63216 100644
--- a/index.html
+++ b/index.html
@@ -2230,9 +2230,9 @@
     <!-- Funnel position: where LUPO sits, and who runs it -->
     <section class="page-section">
         <div class="statement">
-            <h2>Marketing generates the demand.<br>Reps close the deals.<br>LUPO runs everything in between.</h2>
-            <p class="lx-desk">Every call, form, email and chat, answered in seconds, qualified, and booked or routed. Nothing leaks, and no rep time goes to triage. Run it from sales, marketing or RevOps.</p>
-            <p class="lx-mob">Every lead answered in seconds, qualified, and booked or routed. Nothing leaks. No rep time lost to triage.</p>
+            <h2>Marketing generates the demand.<br>Sales closes the deals.<br>LUPO runs the inbound qualification layer in between.</h2>
+            <p class="lx-desk">Every web form, email, chat, and call is answered in seconds, qualified against your ICP, and either booked, routed, or filtered. Real buyers move forward. Vendors, support requests, spam, tire-kickers, and wrong-fit prospects stay out of your reps' calendars. Run it from sales, marketing, or RevOps.</p>
+            <p class="lx-mob">Every lead answered in seconds, qualified against your ICP, then booked, routed, or filtered. Vendors, spam, and wrong-fit prospects stay out of your reps' calendars.</p>
         </div>
 
